title: Australian [colour] diary. No. 026
brief_description: Sydney artists Geoff Pike and Bob Booth exhibit their paintings on a floating gallery, the “One Step”, and profits from sales are to finance further their voyage around the Pacific Islands. Also featured is the launching of the Blue Streak Rocket from Woomera, the holiday resort of Forster on the New South Wales coast with its history, scenic surroundings and facilities.
